General place to centralize mission ideas that nobody's bothered making yet.

Players paradrop behind enemy lines with the intent to set up a massive vehicle ambush. Caches are destroyed and noise created until a large armored QRF is sent, which is then derailed and wiped out by CAS, followed by a long-form evac under fire. - Chirp

Defend an IDAP convoy from guerillas trying to steal supplies - Groovy
